overview: 6 French artists and their teams, made up of young singers, compete in an exceptional show. Each of these teams will be made up of talented children who are fans of an artist. These singers will compete in breathtaking duels, surrounded by children who will all wear the same outfit as their mentor, like "mini-them". And, at the end, only one team and its Mentor will be declared the winner!
